WEBVTT

00:00:00.952 --> 00:00:03.476
Želim započeti eksperimentom.

00:00:04.857 --> 00:00:08.307
Pustit ću vam tri snimke kišnog dana.

00:00:08.935 --> 00:00:12.819
No, u jednoj snimci je zamijenjen zvuk,

00:00:12.843 --> 00:00:15.217
pa sam umjesto zvuka kiše

00:00:15.241 --> 00:00:18.309
dodao zvuk slanine dok se prži.

00:00:19.137 --> 00:00:23.109
Želim da dobro razmislite
koja snimka sadrži taj zvuk slanine.

00:00:23.695 --> 00:00:25.607
(Pada kiša)

00:00:27.394 --> 00:00:29.300
(Pada kiša)